metadata.name: En Vouge
metadata.description: In retrofurutism, people have recently started carrying blood as if it were a designer handbag. In any case, there is one thing in common - there is usually blood on both. The only downside, however, is that it's hard to spot a killer among all the "blood-wearing" trendsetters these days. Considering the picture, the question even arises whether the permissive lady has a bloodthirsty secret or just fashion taste?
